OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to murdering
OL,7,Fhis wife and dumping her body parts in
OL,8,Fa river.
OL,10,FNicholas Metson, 28, was due to stand
OL,11,Ftrial for the murder of 26-year-old
OL,12,FHolly Bramley.
OL,14,FHer body parts were found in the River
OL,15,FWitham, 12 miles from her home, in
OL,16,FMarch last year.
OL,18,FMetson had admitted conspiracy to
OL,19,Fpervert the course of justice by
OL,20,Fdisposing of Ms Bramley's body on 25
OL,21,FMarch.
