OL,6,FHe had denied her murder, but changed
OL,7,Fhis plea to guilty when he appeared at
OL,8,FLincoln Crown Court on Friday for a
OL,9,Fpre-trial hearing.
OL,11,FA large number of Ms Bramley's family
OL,12,Fwere in the public gallery to watch
OL,13,FMetson enter his plea.
OL,15,FMetson, who wore a grey top and grey
OL,16,Fjogging bottoms, will be sentenced on
OL,17,F5 April, alongside 27-year-old Joshua
OL,18,FHancock.
