OL,6,FGordon Aspden KC, prosecuting, asked
OL,7,Ffor the case to be adjourned for the
OL,8,Fdefence to submit a short medical
OL,9,Freport on behalf of Metson and for the
OL,10,Fprosecution and defence to provide
OL,11,Fsentencing notes to the court.
OL,13,FAllison Summers KC, defending Metson,
OL,14,Fasked for a short adjournment for the
OL,15,Fpreparation of a report by an autism
OL,16,Fspecialist.
OL,18,FMs Bramley and Metson are believed to
OL,19,Fhave met at Boston College in
OL,20,FLincolnshire in 2016 and married in
OL,21,F2021.
